title: Getallmaps Offline Map Maker v4.03-TeamGBZ
description:
Offline Map Maker is a tool that help you to get offline    tile images from Google Maps, Yahoo maps, Bing maps. All     downloaded offline images are saved on your disk. You can     view downloaded offline map by Offline Map Viewer. And you   can zoom out or zoom in the offline map, or output the  offline map as a BMP file. If you want to make a offline   map of your city by yourself, it can help you.
Notes
============
1]Install using exe
2]Aplly crack from crack folder
